maps/jungle/clearing/interior/chiefs-hou.orig: Is that the source of wicked kittens?!
maps/jungle/clearing/interior/chiefs-hou.text: Это и есть источник злых котят?!

maps/jungle/clearing/interior/chiefs-hou.orig: Indeed! Summoning evil black cats on poor villagers! This can't stand!!
maps/jungle/clearing/interior/chiefs-hou.text: Ну и ну! Призывать злых чёрных кошек на бедных жителей! Такое нельзя терпеть!!

maps/jungle/clearing/interior/chiefs-hou.orig: Looks like those were the last of them.
Indeed! Were they really an extension of the power plant? Very mysterious!
maps/jungle/clearing/interior/chiefs-hou.text: Ну и ну! Они действительно были частью электростанции? Очень загадочно!

maps/jungle/clearing/interior/chiefs-hou.orig: Let's return to that K'tara girl for now.
maps/jungle/clearing/interior/chiefs-hou.text: Давайте теперь вернёмся к этой девушке, К'таре.
